OL,3,CBusiness adviser warns about a
OL,4,C'tsunami of underfunded pensioners'
OL,6,FA business adviser has joined calls
OL,7,Ffor Jersey to introduce a mandatory
OL,8,Fworkplace pension scheme, warning
OL,9,Fthere would otherwise be "a tsunami of
OL,10,Funderfunded pensioners in the future".
OL,12,FKevin Keen also highlighted the risks
OL,13,Fof an aging population as he warned
OL,14,F"Jersey's really lagging and that
OL,15,Fcannot continue".
OL,17,FThe UK has had such a scheme for more
OL,18,Fthan a decade, while Guernsey
OL,19,Fintroduced one last year - although
OL,20,Fworkers can opt out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
