OL,3,CBusiness adviser warns about a
OL,4,C'tsunami of underfunded pensioners'
OL,6,FGuernsey officials decided the minimum
OL,7,Fsalary contribution is 1% from
OL,8,Femployers and 1.5% from employees.
OL,9,FThere are plans for that to rise to
OL,10,F3.5% and 6.5% respectively.
OL,12,FJersey's new government say that just
OL,13,F30% of all workers have access to a
OL,14,Fprivate or occupational pension.
OL,16,FChief Minister Lyndon Farnham told ITV
OL,17,FNews that whilst he could not
OL,18,Fguarantee bringing in a mandatory
OL,19,Fscheme during the next administration,
OL,20,F"it is something that will be on the
OL,21,Fagenda".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
