OL,3,CBusiness adviser warns about a
OL,4,C'tsunami of underfunded pensioners'
OL,6,FNot everyone is on board with the
OL,7,Fplans. Some businesses say that costs
OL,8,Fare already too high and they are
OL,9,Fsuffering from growing inflation.
OL,11,FCafe owner Jo Baker told ITV News that
OL,12,F90% of his kitchen staff are not from
OL,13,FJersey and the majority have "no hope
OL,14,For expectation of ever retiring" in
OL,15,Fthe island.
OL,17,FHe said that while "he would love to
OL,18,Fsit down and work with people on it",
OL,19,Fhe "cannot see how it is applicable to
OL,20,Fhospitality".
OL,26,@sD@Drr
